snippet.title: EE Builds The Scythe
snippet.description:
SO COOL! Build the Scythe with EE and see how fun, easy, and engaging Snap Ships are. Collect them all so you can Build to Battle! Download the free Snap Ships app and get digital building instructions for the core Snap Ships kits, as well as an endless assortment of custom ships unique to the app. Track your collection, prep ships for flight in Augmented Reality, and test fire your ship's weapons as you battle against the Komplex!
 
Subscribe to our channel to watch new episodes of the original 8-part digital series Snap Ships Dawn of Battle and go behind-the-scenes, get sneak peeks, and even meet the creators! 

Now YOU can Build to Battle! Snap Ships is a versatile building toy with action play. All sets and pieces are interchangeable, so kids can build however they want. Available at Target, Amazon, and Walmart.

snippet.title: Toy Story 3
snippet.description: The creative minds behind Disney•Pixar's groundbreaking animated blockbusters invite you back inside the toy box for a heartwarming and hilarious movie you'll never forget. In Toy Story 3, Woody (voiced by Tom Hanks), Buzz Lightyear (voiced by Tim Allen) and the rest of the Toy Story gang return for an all-new adventure, along with a few new faces – some plastic, some plush – including Barbie's counterpart Ken (voiced by Michael Keaton), a thespian hedgehog named Mr. Pricklepants (voiced by Timothy Dalton) and a strawberry-scented bear named Lots-o'-Huggin' Bear (voiced by Ned Beatty). It's "the biggest, best, most exciting Toy Story of them all," raves Access Hollywood's Scott Mantz.As Andy prepares to depart for college, Woody, Buzz, Jessie and the rest of Andy's faithful toys wonder what will become of them. But, when a mix-up lands them at Sunnyside Daycare, they meet a host of new toys and soon discover a wild new adventure is just beginning!

snippet.title: Rusty Rivets Botasaur Dinosaur Spin Master Toy Unboxing Review || Keith's Toy Box
snippet.description:
Combine it and design it with Rusty Rivets! Now you can bring Rusty’s iconic dinosaur to life with Botasaur. Use the tools and parts included in this set to create rustified fun! Once built, this dinosaur can transform into a vehicle for hours of imaginative and creative play!

This easy-to-build set allows kids to combine it and design it just like Rusty! Rusty fans will develop their logic, building and fine motor skills as they assemble the parts of the Botasaur. Once created, kids can let their imagination run wild as they play with their favorite dinosaur!

A Rusty Rivets unboxing, demo and review by Keith's Toy Box.

Click here for more Rusty Rivets Toys:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfUxTWckfQK2Hsmfwd6bECELOHfZvjOII

RUSTY RIVETS Complete Toys from Spin Master Rivet Lab, Botasaur || Keith's Toy Box
https://youtu.be/583gnDKKDE4

Rusty Rivets is a Canadian CGI interactive animated television series produced by Arc Productions and Spin Master Entertainment for Treehouse TV and Nickelodeon Productions. Inspired by elements of the maker culture, it follows the adventures of a young inventor named Rusty and his team of customized robots. A boy named Rusty Rivets uses his knowledge of engineering to repurpose machine parts and create gadgets. He lives in the city of Sparkton Hills along with his friend Ruby Ramirez, a robotic tyrannosaurid named Botasaur, and a group of smaller robots known as the Bits. The show highlights a variety of concepts related to basic science and technology.

Rusty uses the recurring catch phrase "modify, customize, Rustify" when personalizing inventions. Ruby changes the last word to "Rubify" when she does the alterations.


=========================================

A toy review by Keith's Toy Box, a magical bottomless toy box that reveals a new surprise toy everyday!  Enjoy kid-friendly videos for babies, infants, toddlers, pre-school and primary school children. Watch unboxing, exciting demos, in slow motion, and time lapse, and play with these tried and tested toys from Hot Wheels, Thomas, Chuggington, Mega Bloks, Lego, Duplo, to Takara, Tomy, Tomica, Plarail, Disney Toys, Pixar Disney Cars, and Sesame Street! Great toy reviews for toy collectors young and old alike.

snippet.title: LEGO Chima Maula's Ice Mammoth Stomper 70145 Kids Toy Review & Unboxing
snippet.description:
LEGO Chima Maula's Ice Mammoth Stomper 70145 Kids Toy Review & Unboxing

The icy bad guys from the Mammoth and Saber-tooth tribes are getting away with the CHI in Maula’s Ice Mammoth Stomper. With a weapon in its trunk plus 2 ice blaster cannons and hidden flick missiles, this is one fearsome armored vehicle. Give chase with Worriz on his fire slider and Razar, avoiding the mighty Stomper’s powerful legs and giant feet. Move fast to grab back the CHI before Mottrot launches the Mammoth’s detachable flyer and they escape. 

Includes 6 minifigures with assorted weapons: Maula, Mottrot, Strainor, Vornon, Razar and Worriz
Features a posable trunk with weapon, ice tusks and ribs, posable legs, giant feet, cockpit with space for a mammoth minifigure and hi-tech dashboard, command area, ice prison, 2 weapon racks with a spear, sword, wrench and hammer, ladder and translucent elements plus detachable flyer with 2 flick missiles and cannons, rotating propellers and cockpit with space for a mammoth minifigure
Also includes a fire slider vehicle for Worriz and CHI
Weapons include a Tuskstaff for Maula, Mamzooka for Mottrot, Triple Freeza for Strainor, Chokize for Vornon, Insinasabre for Razar and a Howlthrowa for Worriz
Place Maula in the command area
Pose the trunk
Launch the flyer and shoot the flick missiles
Sneak up on the Ice Mammoth Stomper in Worriz’s vehicle
Maula’s Ice Mammoth Stomper measures over 8" (21cm) high, 15" (40cm) long and 4" (11cm) wide
Detachable flyer measures over 1" (4cm) high, 12" (33cm) long and 11" (28cm) wide
Fire slider measures over 3" (10cm) long and 1" (4cm) wide and under 1" (3cm) high

snippet.title: RC4WD Unboxing & RC First Run  - RTR 4WD Realistic RC Truck
snippet.description:
You know how we do it - straight up unbox and run! This RC4WD Desert Runner RTR 4WD Scale Truck w/Hero Body & 2.4GHz Radio (Black) is a realistic RC truck that can still do a little crawling and bashing!  We give our honest RC first impressions as we RC Unbox and give an RC toy review on this new 1/10 scale RC trophy truck and take it on its RC First Run.  We love this RC toys unboxing, because of all of our RC trucks, this RC4WD Hero is the most RC scale truck we own so far.  

This RC4WD scale truck features a hard plastic body, chassis mounted servo, independent front suspension, a leaf sprung solid rear axle, full interior and remote locking front and rear differentials. This off road truck has other features like reservoir shocks, functional light buckets, and a full interior with complete dash assembly and more.  Lucky for us, this RC4WD Ford Raptor truck is RTR with electronics pre-installed - so batteries in and ride!!

snippet.title: Hand Controlled Flying Saucer UFO w IR and LED Lights - Unboxing Demo Review
snippet.description:
It's so easy to fly this Hand-Controlled Flying Saucer UFO with Infrared (IR) and LED Lights!  Just wave your hand under it to make it fly, no need for a remote control!  It works by infrared (IR) technology that detects any surface below it and makes it hover and rise up!  It has a foam body that lets it withstand falls, crashes, or bounce of walls!  Its flashing LED lights makes it really COOL to fly at night! Other than just your hand, you can also try more advanced tricks like using your legs, knees, arms or shoulders!  Use the catching stick to play catch with friends and toss it back and forth!    Similar to Vectron Wave or Air Hogs or Air Eagle UFO Flyers
- Easy-to-fly hand-controlled Flying Saucer, UFO, perfect for beginners, no need for remote control
- Works by Infrared (IR) technology that detects any surface and makes it hover and rise up!
- Foam body lets it withstand falls and crashes, or lets it bounce of walls!
- Flashing LED lights make it really cool to fly at night!
- Other than your hand, you can also use your legs, knees, arms or shoulders!
- Play catch with friends and toss it back and forth with the use of the catching stick!
- Comes with USB charging cable and built-in rechargeable lithium batteries, charge for 20 minutes, good for 3-7 minutes of flying time.
- Fly indoors or outdoors, but keep away from people's faces, eyes, animals, and fragile objects.

Available at Banggood here:
http://www.banggood.com/Flying-Saucer-UFO-Hand-Induced-Hovering-And-Floating-Flight-With-LED-p-962129.html?utm_source=panxiaohong&utm_medium=Keith&utm_campaign=panxiaohong

More videos of flying toys here
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfUxTWckfQK1rlGSqYbWBRXh9qws6GivU

snippet.title: The Baa-Baa Barn from John Crane Unboxing & Toy Review
snippet.description:
In this episode of the Fun Kids Toy Club, presenters Bex and Sean are unboxing the Baa-Baa Barn from John Crane Ltd and giving their toy review.

This toy is a big old barn with loads of different farm animals like a cow, horse, sheep, pig, a little rabbit and quite a few other animals too as Bex discovers!

Sean also gets very excited when he finds out that when the animals head into the barn they break into song!

Although Sean also shows why you should never trust him with ANY toy, not even one made for children aged 2 years plus!

You can find out more about the children's radio station, Fun Kids at http://www.funkidslive.com
